hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: A book of First Class stamps the mental health miracles “The industry is still male dominated. I think it has worked more to our advantage to be honest. There was probably a bit of novelty value at first but when they tasted the beer they said, 'This is all right, it’s good’. We probably produce at full production about 130 nine-gallon casks a week. There’s 72 pints in each of those casks. We just employed another brewer to help us expand.”
